{"tid":1887010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長者：「印度人好嘢，香港政府同中國人無能」","createTime":"2020-02-19T09:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T10:27:35.000Z","uid":51271,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"cbbe8eeb44c6bcdca2984e70930627387df866ae","tid":1887010,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:27:06.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情持續，投疫物資短缺，市民「一罩難求」。九龍印度廟今日下午於尖沙咀河內道免費向長者派發 21,000 個口罩，每人憑籌號可獲 20 個口罩。活動原定下午 3 時開始，但鑑於排隊人數眾多，需要提早半小時開始派發，有不少排隊長者表示「印度人真係好」，「現場又有秩序」，更有長者指「印度人好嘢，香港政府同中國人無能」...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%B4%BE%E9%80%BE%E4%BA%8C%E8%90%AC%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E4%BA%88%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85-%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E5%BB%9F%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-%E6%88%91%E9%83%BD%E4%BF%82%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA-%E6%83%B3%E5%B9%AB%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E9%2580%25BE%25E4%25BA%258C%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E4%25BA%2588%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585-%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%25BB%259F%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E6%2588%2591%25E9%2583%25BD%25E4%25BF%2582%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%2583%25B3%25E5%25B9%25AB%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%2F&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5HpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=51dd0f37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E9%2580%25BE%25E4%25BA%258C%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E4%25BA%2588%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2580%2585-%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E5%25BB%259F%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E6%2588%2591%25E9%2583%25BD%25E4%25BF%2582%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%2583%25B3%25E5%25B9%25AB%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%2F&h=9b996f9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%B4%BE%E9%80%BE%E4%BA%8C%E8%90%AC%E5%8F